    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Computer System Diagram Feedback\r\n\r\nOnce you've used the planning template in order to diagram out your proposed computer system, use this AI Chat in order to get feedback on how you might iterate on your design.\r\n\r\n1. Download an image of your diagram as a **.PNG**\r\n2. Choose **Upload > From Device** and select your diagram\r\n\r\nChat with the AI to:\r\n\r\n* Learn strategies and methods to make your diagram clearer\r\n* Ask for ways to ways to increase or expand your system's functionality\r\n* Learn about different components that you might add",
